{"cover_image":"../media/blog-social-intro.png","title":"Highly Performant React theming with CSS variables(With Intellisense <img class=\"emoji\" draggable=\"false\" alt=\"ðŸ˜‰\" src=\"https://twemoji.maxcdn.com/v/13.1.0/svg/1f609.svg\"/>)","date":"2021-07-04T18:30:00.000Z","description":"Theme your React app with confidence, while also keeping the performance high","body":"<p>Theming in React is an enigma. You'll find a thousand articles on different ways of theming in React. Some suggest going full JavaScript, using the context API. Some suggest going full CSS with just CSS Variables. All these are really great approaches in some very fine articles. So why another article on this topic then?</p>\n<p>This article aims to marry both the JS and CSS approaches into one single approach: <strong>The performance of raw CSS, and the great Developer Experience of JavaScript <img class=\"emoji\" draggable=\"false\" alt=\"ðŸ”¥\" src=\"https://twemoji.maxcdn.com/v/13.1.0/svg/1f525.svg\"></strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"\" alt=\"I request elaboration meme\" style=\"display: none;\"></p><div class=\"picture-container\">\n  <div class=\"gif-vid-container\">\n    <video autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\">\n      <source src=\"../media/react-theming-css-vars--i-request-elaboration-vision/vidgif.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n      Your browser doesn't support HTML5 video playback. <a href=\"../media/react-theming-css-vars--i-request-elaboration-vision.gif\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">See the gif here</a>\n    </video>\n  </div>\n  </div><p></p>\n<h1 id=\"Elaboration\"><a class=\"heading-link\" href=\"#Elaboration\">#</a>Elaboration</h1>\n<h2 id=\"About-CSS-Variables-method\"><a class=\"heading-link\" href=\"#About-CSS-Variables-method\">#</a>About CSS Variables method</h2>\n<p>This is how you would theme your site using just CSS variables</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki\" style=\"background-color: #292D3E\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">body</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">light</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">  --app-color-primary</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> blue</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">  --app-color-primary-rgb</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">0</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">,</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">0</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">,</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">255</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">  --app-color-primary-contrast</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> white</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">  --app-color-light</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> white</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">  --app-color-light-rgb</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">255</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">,</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">255</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">,</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">255</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">  --app-color-light-contrast</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> black</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">  --app-color-dark</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> black</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">  --app-color-dark-rgb</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">0</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">,</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">0</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">,</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">0</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">  --app-color-dark-contrast</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> white</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">body</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">dark</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">  --app-color-primary</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> blue</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">  --app-color-primary-rgb</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">0</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">,</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">0</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">,</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">255</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">  --app-color-primary-contrast</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> white</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">  --app-color-light</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> black</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">  --app-color-light-rgb</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">0</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">,</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">0</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">,</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">0</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">  --app-color-light-contrast</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> white</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">  --app-color-dark</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> black</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">  --app-color-dark-rgb</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">0</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">,</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">0</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">,</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F78C6C\">0</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">  --app-color-dark-contrast</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\"> white</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre>\n<p>Theming using CSS variables is extremely fast. It's as if you're reaching into the internals of browser and manually repainting the DOM, without the tediousness that a process as complex as manually repainting requires. All you have to do is change the variables, and the whole page repaints itself extremely fast, totally jank-free.</p>\n","id":"react-theming-css-vars","reading_time":1.4,"toc":[{"indent":0,"id":"Elaboration","title":"#Elaboration","length":12},{"indent":1,"id":"About-CSS-Variables-method","title":"#About CSS Variables method","length":27}],"seriesIndex":0}